FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a coin dispensing apparatus of the present invention with a detector assembly integrated into the perimeter opening of a hopper;


FIG. 2 is a schematic diagram disclosing the interface of the light grid pattern with a computer-based control system;


FIG. 3 is a flow diagram to explain one possible operation of the embodiment of FIG. 2; and


FIG. 4 is a perspective view of a prior art coin dispensing structure.
